net.gaborszita.realisticelevator.elevator

Class Elevator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.gaborszita.realisticelevator.elevator.Elevator

  • public class Elevator
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an elevator. It is responsible for handling the elevator's movement, fulfilling stop requests, and opening its doors.
